{"tid":1762820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毋忘831恐襲 3個月","createTime":"2019-11-30T00:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T13:40:05.000Z","uid":143295,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2f2b3148d2252225399362b662ae2ae097bf1f","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:56:31.000Z","msg":"成個熱門竟然冇一個post 講831 3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連日程表都冇一個活動係關831事<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪已經唔記得警曱點樣對待我地嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家係咪已經唔記得警曱點樣無差別攻擊平民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地連公開cctv都未做到 <br />\n831嘅真相都未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區選贏左係開心<br />\n人權法過左係開心<br />\n但係千其唔好唔記得，呢啲全部都係用手足嘅血換返架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n831義士唔係condom啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚我要見到大家<br />\n太子站見！ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日未搵到真相 我地一日都唔可以放棄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nu5QjUu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNu5QjUu.jpg&h=574d95ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推我上去！ <br />\n利申：第一次開po 有咩做錯屌得細力啲"},{"pid":"1dc4944828fbf34c0641b4be174600475815cc5f","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:56:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc0d82993074d1f8cf8d750dddfadd280b2fd579","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:57:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e388782162691579287e18fc46c7d747eb513ba","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:57:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7f24ec710a8ba02451c9660de12ddbcf77c1452","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:57:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e662d403bfed959ce6aa15ec56950a208dd63f0","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:57:47.000Z","msg":"手足唔係condom啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad01e03ecb2daccc609668fe91ab26e2ec11467e","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749ba097a4600f89215786bc2c18bdecbad5f43b","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40f0bd6c100ee193b8b3b4ce6e9cd439cbf6703e","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:58:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c8299053bf8910b39b2e31c7a62559931cfbe57","tid":1762820,"uid":143295,"lik